  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>A hot and cold buffet breakfast will be served at The Garden Grill &amp; Bar restaurant. During this service, you can also have your eggs or omelettes "cooked to order" at the live breakfast station. </p>
<p>In the evening, you'll have a three-course meal consisting of local traditional dishes, with a choice of main. </p>
<p>After dinner, head to the lobby bar for a drink or two. </p>
<p><strong>Dress code for the restaurant:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Informal</li>
</ul>]]></cateringDescription>
