  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hilton Garden Inn is a stunning property that stands out from the crowd, with wooden-slat balconies overlooking either the Swiss Alps or city itself. It brings a modern charm to the promenade with an alpine coloured façade, and you can always rely on a comfy bed to come back to at the end of the day. Since opening in 2012, the stylish rooms and excellent facilities have been a hit for those seeking an active or relaxing stay. </p>
<h2>Wellness facilities</h2>
<p>Featuring a sauna and steam room, you can recharge your batteries and relax your body after a day of exploring the local landscape. With an indoor fitness centre you can focus on core, cardio or strength workouts to get a head start on your day. All rooms include coffee making facilities, creating the ideal setup for you to sit back and relax on the balcony. </p>
<h2>Great location </h2>
<p>Perfectly situated between the Davos Dorf and Davos Platz train stations, this hotel is just the right distance to the village with easy access to public transport from the moment you step outside of the lobby.  Reach the Weissfluhjoch in no time via the Parsenn funicular, just a short walk away. </p>]]></description>
