  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Twin or Double Rooms</strong> are around 24m² and sleep one to two people.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have: </strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony or terrace </li>
<li>Tv with English speaking channels </li>
<li>Tea &amp; coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>Safe </li>
<li>Minibar/fridge</li>
<li>Hair dryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in: <strong>3pm</strong></li>
<li>Check-out: <strong>12pm</strong></li>
</ul>
